      <ID>84</ID>
      <DefaultText>The hands back away from you, eyes wide with fear. "We didn't mean anything by it, captain," [Specified 3] whines.

[Specified 1] strikes a baton against the mast. "You heard the captain! Get back to your stations!"

The crew breaks apart, glancing to one another while avoiding your gaze. You've averted the crisis, for the moment.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
